reviewText: EXCELLENT PERSON TO DEAL WITH! THANK YOU

I thoroughly enjoyed this concert, with the exception of the song sub-titles and that the fact that it is rather short. It is so difficult to find recorded Supertramp performances, especially since they were all taken down from YouTube.
I know it will be great. Bought for a Christmas present. Have not viewed yet. Price was just right. We have waited so long for Supertramp to come to DVD. Finally!
